[I] Alternative minimalist taskbar for Xfce

[T] Docklike Taskbar behaves similarly to many other desktop environments and
[T] operating systems. Wherein all application windows are grouped together as
[T] an icon and can be pinned to act as a launcher when the application is not
[T] running. Commonly referred to as a dock.

[U] https://docs.xfce.org/panel-plugins/xfce4-docklike-plugin/start

